FBIS3-7201 "dreas058_c_94021" FBIS-EAS-94-058 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Mar 1994 North Korea Kim Chong-il Sends Thanks to Radio, TV Staff SK2503045594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0433 GMT 25 Mar 94 SK2503045594 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, March 25 (KCNA) -- The dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il sent thanks to the creating staff of serial TV dramas of the Radio and TV Broadcasting Committee of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea. The staff has created many serial TV dramas conforming to the intention of the party and the demand of the people. They produced 9 dramas of 80 parts including "Joy" and "The Morning on the Plateau" over the past one year.
